Actions.Text: REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Clarifies the status of squatters for purposes of removal proceedings
Summary: Clarifies that a squatter is not a tenant for purposes of removal proceedings.
LawSection: Real Property Actions and Proceedings Law
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the real property actions and proceedings law, in relation to clarifying the status of squatters for purposes of removal proceedings
